{"tid":2067391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國安法】英國於聯合國發言　指立法破壞港自治　中國、北韓同聲反對","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T08:32:27.000Z","uid":227801,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d7600200249a8e5db870d725cca04a6778350076","tid":2067391,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%BC%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E6%8C%87%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%90%8C%E8%81%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=9c1096d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%2F&h=2ee9996e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%BC%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E6%8C%87%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%90%8C%E8%81%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D/</a><br />\n儘管多國已發表聲明，指國安法的通過將損害香港的自治，全國人大常委仍將於 6 月 18 日起，一連&nbsp;3 日討論「港版國安法」細節。作為香港的前宗主國及《中英聯合聲明》其中一個簽訂方，英國亦多次在此事上發聲。據路透社報道，英國駐聯合國大使今日於聯合國人權理事會上，稱中國訂立港版國安法的決定違反《中英聯合聲明》，中方則指責英國干預中國內政。<br />\n英國駐聯合國大使 Julian Braithwaite 表示，中國在《中英聯合聲明》中有其國際義務，促請中方與香港的人民溝通，並保障香港的高度自治、人權和自由。中國駐日內瓦代表蔣端則表明英方干預中國內政，中方將堅決反對。<br />\n蔣端又指，訂立港版國安法只是為了堵塞香港在國家安全上的漏洞，維護國家主權及安全，強調是合法及必要。"},{"pid":"a49a22a8a5931a326ab3a5b930eabd8c5728077f","tid":2067391,"uid":224510,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76413aa4544b91cc3563c26af21ac7e644c956d0","tid":2067391,"uid":353267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"日出了"},{"pid":"8a7f2025cdab956c6e93f27ee31216f590a3cf42","tid":2067391,"uid":126099,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:23:50.000Z","msg":"北韓都係聯合國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd94e190bedaff7bcfb83d35eecb5b567c56af0","tid":2067391,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"北韓"},{"pid":"683b5afec6d655c6f952038044302e30f106e0a7","tid":2067391,"uid":205462,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"即係英國嘅外交政策，就可以被中國同北韓干涉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合國大會上，唔討論別國嘅問題，咁開會嚟托咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba696d602430e6c419fdae9aa047db557283c78d","tid":2067391,"uid":121197,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:33:10.000Z","msg":"英國叫中國保障香港的高度自治、人權和自由<br />\n咁點解中國唔大大聲話國安法就係保障一國兩制、保障人權和自由<br />\n要屌人干預內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"h